OL,3,CPolice admit to Clare's Law failures
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed by partner
OL,6,FThree women have been harmed,
OL,7,Fincluding one who was stabbed and
OL,8,Falmost killed by her partner, after a
OL,9,Fformer Wiltshire Police staff member
OL,10,Ffailed to share details about their
OL,11,Fpartners' past violent behaviours, a
OL,12,Fmisconduct panel has heard.
OL,14,FWiltshire Police have admitted to
OL,15,Ffailing in their duty to protect
OL,16,Fpeople from harm and acknowledged that
OL,17,Fthe incidents might have been
OL,18,Fprevented if the women had been
OL,19,Fprovided with information they
OL,20,Frequested and were legally entitled to.
