OL,3,CPolice admit to Clare's Law failures
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed by partner
OL,6,FA disciplinary held on Wednesday 8
OL,7,FOctober found that the former member
OL,8,Fof police staff would have been
OL,9,Fdismissed for gross misconduct had he
OL,10,Fnot resigned.
OL,12,FGavin Hudson, 40, worked as a
OL,13,Fresearcher responding to requests made
OL,14,Funder Clare's Law, which allows people
OL,15,Fto apply for information about their
OL,16,Fpartner's past if they are concerned
OL,17,Fthey may have a history of abuse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
