OL,6,FSeven allegations were upheld against
OL,7,Fhim and he has been barred from ever
OL,8,Fworking in a policing organisation
OL,9,Fagain.
OL,11,FThe hearing concluded that his
OL,12,Fsafeguarding failures put women at
OL,13,Fcontinued risk of domestic abuse.
OL,15,FOne woman was stabbed and seriously
OL,16,Finjured by her partner after applying
OL,17,Fto Wiltshire Police for information
OL,18,Fabout his past.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
