OL,3,CPolice admit to Clare's Law failures
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed by partner
OL,6,FHer partner had violence warning
OL,7,Fmarkers against his name, which Hudson
OL,8,Ffailed to identify. The partner was
OL,9,Fconvicted of attempted murder in 2023.
OL,11,FAnother woman was abused by her
OL,12,Fpartner after Hudson failed to
OL,13,Fidentify his previous convictions for
OL,14,Fdomestic assault.
OL,16,FA total of 33 failures by Wiltshire
OL,17,FPolice to uphold Clare's Law were
OL,18,Ffound in a review of 3,778
OL,19,Fapplications submitted between 2015
OL,20,Fand 2023.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
