OL,3,CPolice admit to Clare's Law failures
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed by partner
OL,6,FThese included instances when a
OL,7,Fperson's history of violence or abuse
OL,8,Fwas not disclosed to their partner,
OL,9,Finadequate research was carried out or
OL,10,Fthere were administrative failures.
OL,12,FHudson had previously been based in
OL,13,Fthe control room and contact centre
OL,14,Fbefore moving to a research role with
OL,15,Fa domestic abuse support team in 2015.
OL,17,FThe force said after referrals were
OL,18,Fmade about him in 2019 and 2020 he
OL,19,Freceived management advice, and an
OL,20,Faudit of his work was undertaken.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
