OL,3,CPolice admit to Clare's Law failures
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed by partner
OL,6,FChief Constable Catherine Roper said:
OL,7,F"We have failed in our primary duty to
OL,8,Fprotect people from harm, and I cannot
OL,9,Foveremphasise the depth of the apology
OL,10,FI issued when we first found out about
OL,11,Fthese critical service failures.
OL,13,F"Gavin Hudson's dereliction of duty
OL,14,Fhas no doubt undermined the trust and
OL,15,Fconfidence our communities have in our
OL,16,Fsafeguarding processes, and I
OL,17,Funderstand that.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
