OL,3,CPolice admit to Clare's Law failures
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed by partner
OL,6,F"We have changed our leadership in
OL,7,Fthis area of our organisation and now
OL,8,Fhave more intrusive supervision of
OL,9,Fthis process.
OL,11,F"We will ensure ongoing organisational
OL,12,Fimprovements will be made as a result
OL,13,Fof the learning from these serious
OL,14,Ffailures."
OL,16,FWilshire Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,17,FPhilip Wilkinson said he was "deeply
OL,18,Ftroubled" by the situation.
