OL,3,CPolice admit to Clare's Law failures
OL,4,Cafter woman stabbed by partner
OL,6,F"To the women affected - and to the
OL,7,Fwider public - I want to say: I am
OL,8,Fsorry. You were failed. The systems
OL,9,Fmeant to protect you broke down and
OL,10,Findividuals did not do their duty to
OL,11,Ftheir fullest. That must never happen
OL,12,Fagain," he said.
OL,14,F"This case is a stark reminder of the
OL,15,Fneed for rigorous training,
OL,16,Fsupervision and a culture of
OL,17,Faccountability within policing.
